OL,6,FGovernment spending has hit its
OL,7,Fhighest level in six decades,
OL,8,Faccording to ONS figures, as Jasmine
OL,9,FCameron Chileshe reports
OL,11,FGovernment borrowing is at its
OL,12,F"highest level since the 1960s" says
OL,13,Fthe Treasury, ahead of new Chancellor
OL,14,FRachel Reeves' first Budget.
OL,16,FChief Secretary to the Treasury Darren
OL,17,FJones said: "When we came into office,
OL,18,Fwe inherited an economy that wasn't
OL,19,Fworking for working people.
