OL,6,F"Today's data shows the highest August
OL,7,Fborrowing on record outside the
OL,8,Fpandemic. Debt is 100% of GDP, the
OL,9,Fhighest level since the 1960s."
OL,11,FBorrowing rose to #13.7 billion last
OL,12,Fmonth, marking the third highest
OL,13,FAugust on record, driven by higher
OL,14,Fspending on public services due to
OL,15,Fincreased running costs and pay
OL,16,Fincreases.
OL,18,FThe increase means public sector debt
OL,19,Fhit 100% of gross domestic product
OL,20,F(GDP) at the end of August 2024.
