OL,6,F"Because of the #22 billion black hole
OL,7,Fin our public finances we have
OL,8,Finherited this year alone, we are
OL,9,Ftaking the tough decisions now to fix
OL,10,Fthe foundations of our economy, so we
OL,11,Fcan rebuild Britain and make every
OL,12,Fpart of the country better off," Mr
OL,13,FJones said.
OL,15,FThe figure, which excludes public
OL,16,Fsector banks, means national debt is
OL,17,Fat levels last seen in the early
OL,18,F1960s, the Office for National
OL,19,FStatistics (ONS) said.
