OL,6,FONS chief economist Grant Fitzner
OL,7,Fsaid: "Borrowing was up by over #3
OL,8,Fbillion last month on 2023's figure,
OL,9,Fand was the third highest August
OL,10,Fborrowing on record.
OL,12,F"Central Government tax receipts grew
OL,13,Fstrongly, but this was outweighed by
OL,14,Fhigher expenditure, largely driven by
OL,15,Fbenefits uprating and higher spending
OL,16,Fon public services due to increased
OL,17,Frunning costs and pay."
OL,19,FThe ONS said public sector borrowing
OL,20,Fwas #3.3 billion more than in August
OL,21,Flast year.
